section(class="hero is-dark")
    div(class="hero-body")
        div(class="container")
            h1(class="title") Hello, my name is Steven Waters.     
            p(class="intro-text") I'm a full-stack developer with a passion for front-end development, UI, and UX. The languages I know best are HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, and PHP.
section(class="section")
    div(class="container")
        h1(class="title") Skills
        //h2(class="subtitle") (w = working knowledge, b = basic knowledge)
        div(class="tabs is-toggle is-toggle-rounded")
            ul
                - var i = 0
                each categoryObj, categoryName in skills
                    - var classList = (i === 0) ? "tab is-active" : "tab"
                    li(class=classList)
                        a(href="#tab-" + i)= categoryName
                    - i++
        - var i = 0
        each categoryObj, categoryName in skills
            - var classList = (i === 0) ? "tab-content is-active" : "tab-content"
            div(id="tab-" + i, class=classList)
                h3=categoryName
                each skillLevel, name in categoryObj
                    h4=name
                    progress(class="progress is-large" value=skillLevel max="100") 60%
            - i++
section(class="section")
    div(class="container")
        h1(class="title") Projects
        p(class="subtitle") Unfortantely, I don't have a lot to show off here because my professional work involved working on applications that are propietary and internal/semi-intranet apps. All of the projects I worked on from home were usually experimentations so they were never completed fully (sorry, not sorry).
        div(class="tile is-ancestor", style="flex-wrap: wrap")
            each project in projects
                - var classList = (projects.length < 3) ? 'tile is-parent is-4' : 'tile is-parent is-4'
                div(class=classList)
                    div(class="tile project is-child box has-text-centered")
                        figure(class="image image is-square")
                            img(class="project-screenshot", src='images/screenshots-resized/' + project.thumbnailFileName + '.png', alt=project.altText)
                        div(class="project-details")
                            p(class="project-description")= project.descriptionText
                            a(class="button is-primary is-rounded", href=project.url, title=project.linkTitleText)=project.linkText + ' Â»'
section(class="section")
    div(class="container")
        h1(class="title") Get In Touch
